OL,6,FThe family of Christie Harnett told
OL,7,FKatie Cole about the immeasurable
OL,8,Fimpact her death has had on them
OL,10,FThe family of a teenager who died
OL,11,Funder the care of a mental health
OL,12,Ftrust convicted of failing her say
OL,13,Ftheir lives will never be the same
OL,14,Fagain.
OL,16,FChristie Harnett was just 17-years-old
OL,17,Fwhen she took her life while she was a
OL,18,Fpatient at , in , run by the Tees, Esk
OL,19,Fand Wear Valleys NHS Foundation Trust
OL,20,F(TEWV).
