OL,6,FThe youngster, from , in County
OL,7,FDurham, had made a similar attempt on
OL,8,Fher life just three months before her
OL,9,Fdeath in June 2019.
OL,11,FFollowing the sentencing of the trust
OL,12,Fon Friday (19 April) for failing to
OL,13,Fprovide safe care and treatment to
OL,14,FChristie, her family told ITV News
OL,15,FTyne Tees how her death had had an
OL,16,Fimmeasurable impact on them.
OL,18,F"The first death I ever experienced
OL,19,Fwas my own sister," said Ayron
OL,20,FHarnett, who is one of five of
OL,21,FChristie's siblings.
