OL,6,F"What happened has just smashed me,
OL,7,Fand I don't think I'm ever going to
OL,8,Ffind all the little pieces that have
OL,9,Fjust fallen to the ground."
OL,11,FChristie's dad, Michael Harnett, said
OL,12,Fthe scars left from losing his
OL,13,Fdaughter are profound and long-
OL,14,Flasting, and have rippled through
OL,15,Fthose who loved her.
