OL,6,F"Christie's youngest brother at the
OL,7,Ftime, he was only six," he explained.
OL,8,F"It's not something that any family
OL,9,Fmember should be doing, let alone a
OL,10,Fchild having to stand there watching
OL,11,Ftheir sister die in hospital.
OL,13,F"It's going to change them all and
OL,14,Faffect all of them for the rest of
OL,15,Ftheir life."
OL,17,FChristie had first come into contact
OL,18,Fwith the TEWV Trust at the age of 10.
