OL,6,FAn , published in November 2022,
OL,7,Funcovered 49 failings by the trust
OL,8,Frelating to its care of the teenager,
OL,9,Fincluding no plans to manage her risk
OL,10,Fof self harm or investigate her
OL,11,Fprevious attempt on her life in March
OL,12,F2019.
OL,14,FThe report also revealed a failure to
OL,15,Frespond to concerns raised by
OL,16,FChristie, her family and staff, as
OL,17,Fwell as an absence of skilled staff or
OL,18,Ftraining to manage her risk.
