OL,6,FIt was also found that rapid changes
OL,7,Fto staffing, including a mass
OL,8,Fsuspension in November 2018, impacted
OL,9,FChristie's care.
OL,11,FTEWV, was ordered to pay a fine of
OL,12,F#200,000 .
OL,14,FChristie's family say, while this
OL,15,Fbrings them some relief, it's not
OL,16,Fjustice so they are now calling for a
OL,17,Fpublic inquiry.
