OL,6,FEllis Brayley, Christie's sister,
OL,7,Fsaid: "I don't feel like we've got
OL,8,Fexactly what we wanted just yet, as no
OL,9,Fone specifically is going to be held
OL,10,Faccountable.
OL,12,F"I think it's a slap on the wrist and
OL,13,FI don't feel like it's going to make
OL,14,Fany sort of difference towards the
OL,15,Fpeople that were in charge of it all."
OL,17,FMichael added that while the
OL,18,Fsentencing had brought some closure, a
OL,19,Fpublic inquiry was "the only way
OL,20,Fforward".
