OL,6,FThis summer, Christie's family will
OL,7,Fwelcome a new life as her sister Ellis
OL,8,Fis expecting a baby boy - a happy
OL,9,Fmoment that is tinged with sadness.
OL,11,F"I don't have that sisterly bond that
OL,12,Fwe had," she explained.
OL,14,F"When we were growing up, we always
OL,15,Ftalked about having families and
OL,16,Flooking after each other's children
OL,17,Fand she is not here to do that with me
OL,18,Fand she's not here to experience the
OL,19,Fpregnancy, to be there and be the big
OL,20,Faunty that she should be being."
