OL,6,FEllis turned 19 the day before burying
OL,7,FChristie. While she still carries that
OL,8,Fpain, she says she is determined to
OL,9,Fhelp the memory of her sister live on.
OL,11,F"My baby boy will know exactly who she
OL,12,Fwas and how beautiful she was - her
OL,13,Fsmile," she added.
OL,15,F"My baby will definitely know who
OL,16,FChristie was, 100%."
